                            java.lang.String name,
                            int slot,
                            java.lang.Integer... pageArgs)
        adds an ItemStack to the inventory or to a specific window. If an item is in the same slot as this item it gets replaced.
        Parameters:
        mat - Material of the Item
        name - Name of the Item
        slot - Slot the item is in (does not work if a border item is on that slot)
        pageArgs - [Optional] page that the item will be on (enable pages first!)
        Returns:
        Returns the created guiItem
